davinci.data

Interface IData

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, java.io.Serializable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IGraph<N>, IGraphTree<N>, ITable<N>, ITree<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractData, Graph, Table, Tree

    public interface IData
extends java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
    The general data interface. All the data structures used in DaVinci must
    implement this interface.

    Author:
    Nan Cao
